==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wake-robin
<hw>Wake"-rob`in</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any plant of the genus <gen>Arum</gen>, especially, in England, the
cuckoopint (<spn>Arum maculatum</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ In America the name is given to several species of
Trillium, and sometimes to the Jack-in-the-pulpit.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Waketime</ent>⟦br⟧
